summary: This was my first time drawing, inking and painting a giant robot in big details and stuff. So his design is a bit off but hey...
body:
This was my first time drawing, inking and painting a giant robot in big details and stuff. So his design is a bit off but hey it was worth the 83% in my art class.

Also I found out my teacher was a fan of transformers and he thought starscream voice was annoying back in the g1 cartoon.
